      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. This car features a lustrous exterior finish that still catches the light beautifully, with only the slightest evidence of careful road use. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium upholstery is supple and free of tears, while all electronic features\u2014from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, resulting in a smooth, quiet ride and a transmission that shifts effortlessly. Whether you\u2019re commuting through the city or embarking on a long-distance tour, this vehicle offers the confidence of a well-documented maintenance history and the comfort of a smoke-free, tidy interior. It is ready to provide its next owner with years of reliable performance.",
      "price": 38500.0,
