      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a functional M-Variable differential lock. Key mechanical milestones have been addressed, including a Vanos system refresh and structural reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points. The suspension geometry remains true, providing the precise turn-in and telepathic feedback characteristic of the chassis. While showing minor cosmetic road wear, the powertrain and cooling systems are in excellent health, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning enthusiast.",
